{
  "chapter": 37,
  "chapter_summary": "本章中，仇恕与慕容惜生藏在地室，仇恕假冒毛臬应付长孙策，原想套出机密，却被谨慎的长孙策识破。长孙策以银壶暗放千日醉魂香，使二人四肢无力而神智清醒，并趁机揭开慕容惜生面具，欲加侵犯。仇恕凝聚倒地前保存的真力，在千钧一发时一掌击毙长孙策。危机过后，两人贴身相对，在眼波中明白彼此由仇转爱的真情。毛文琪返回寻找丝囊，撞见此景后爱恨交迸，撕碎物件并疯狂嘲讽二人，继而用针线缝合他们手腕，再以毛臬铸造的毒龙圈将二人锁在一起，决意继续折磨这对令她痛苦的男女。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "毛臬与你有仇，她又与你有什么仇恨？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "是以到后来我也放过了她……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "师父。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "text": "进来。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "师父已安歇了么？弟子长孙策有事禀报。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来又是他们门—下的'玉骨'使者'！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "text": "在外面说。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "弟子谨尊师命，将仇独残骨一齐送至杜仲奇杜师叔之处，杜师叔令弟子回来禀报师父。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "text": "杜仲奇说什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父从未在我面前直称杜师叔的名字，今日怎地……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道里面的人并非师父，而是别人冒充的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "杜师叔令弟子禀告师父，就说师父留在他老人家处的十二柄宝刀宝剑，都分配停当了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "text": "知道了，还有什么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师父哪里有十二柄宝刀宝剑，哼哼，好小子，你竟敢冒充师父的声音，来骗我长孙策，叫你知道厉害厂",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "杜师叔已为师父召集了关外二十七名高手，其中还包括了天山与长白两派的剑客，还有……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "text": "还有什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "还有关内陕甘一带的高手，也已被杜师叔联络好了，这些人都对姓仇的怀恨已久，杜师叔一说他们便答应了，就连穷家帮的穷神凌龙，都已被杜师叔以十万两银子收买！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你两人运气倒也不坏，师父令我求这千日醉魂香来，本来对付姓仇的，却被你两人先尝了滋味。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你两人竟敢冒充师父，我少不得要让你们受些活罪，先将你们两只手砍断，再盘问来历。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "原来你们面上还戴着面具，好好，我倒要看看你们究竟是什么变的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你动我一动，我变鬼也要杀死你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_sun_ce",
      "speaker_name": "长孙策",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "软绵绵的身子，倒像个女子似的，你若真是漂亮的女子，大爷倒要将你先乐上一乐，再……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仇恕呀仇恕，早知如此，我就早该将我心中的真情告诉你，你是我一生中惟一使我动了真情的男子……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知如此，我更应将保存了二十多年的贞操，也给了你，那么我纵然死了，也无遗憾了！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不过只见了她一面而已，怎会对她生出情感，我只是已被她不可抗拒的美丽所吸引……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "该死……该死……该死……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "好师姐，你说要为他和我解除冤仇，你说要将他和我拉拢到一起，原来你用的竟是这样奇妙而惊人的法子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你呢？仇公子，你该感激我呀，是不是？\n没有我，你们怎么会在一起？你该谢谢我这媒人才是！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你们为何不说话？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好一个漂亮的人物，难怪我师姐喜欢你！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "呀，这是怎么回事，你们的身子，为什么像棉花——样，嗯嗯，你们不要解释，我看到的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我看到你们的眼睛，你看着我，我看着你……",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好亲热呀，那时若有人将你们的头一齐砍下来，你们也不知道，只可惜我偏偏跑来了……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我不好，都是我不好，夹在你们中间，破坏了你们的事，但你们放心，我一定要补偿你们。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "好了，这样更好……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "不好，这样还不够好，我要让你们一生一世都不能分开才好，好师姐，你说对不对？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "乖乖的，不要动。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你看，我好不好，我把你们连在一起。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "好了，你们永远分不开了……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你看，你的身子里，有了他的血，他的身子里，也有了你的血，你们该不该谢谢我？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "好师姐，你一定认得这东西的，但是……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子，你认不认得呢？这就是我师父用万年寒铁，精心铸造的毒龙圈，她老人家造来本为对付——种最最奇异的野兽的，只要这两边一合，便永远分不开了，宝刀宝剑，也斩不断！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_wen_qi",
      "speaker_name": "毛文琪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好了，真的好了，线可以扯断，这毒龙圈却是永远扯不断的，你们真的永远分不开了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 37,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    }
  ],
